1.0.name: wordpress/free-event-banner
1.0.description:
This plugin are used for managing the banner or any of the blocks which will turn automatically changed when some important event are occur, which this also already set at the back end.

The events date will be continued repeated every years

Features :

  • easy to manage on the back end
  • easy to add on the front end
  • can be used not only on the banner but on any of html block components

Demo :

  • front-end address : http://4test.denovembre.com/event_banner
  • back-end address : http://4test.denovembre.com/event_banner/wp-admin
  • back-end username : demo
  • back-end password : demo

Contact :

If there are a bug, problem or any idea, suggestion, advice. Please e-mail me at : blog@denovembre.com</
